snippet.title: Worldless - Official Gameplay Trailer | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Worldless, the new  2D adventure platformer  from Thunderful, Coatsink, and Noname Studios does more with less in this beautiful gameplay trailer. Explore, fight, and grow in this stylized turn-based adventure, when Worldless launches in 2023.

#IGN #Worldless
